titre: 変態家族 新妻淫乱責め
synopsis: Sexual bombshell Reiko Yamaguchi, star of the smash-hit Japanese Wife Next Door films, is back and this time she needs an exorcist! Is her new husband possessed by a demon or is he just a pervert? And what's up with her father-in-law and his insatiable desire for Reiko? Something is definitely wrong with Reiko's family, and only an exorcist can help! Akira Fukamachi directs this raunchy take on exorcism.
